    },
    {
        "Pierre Savorgnan de Brazza": "Pierre Savorgnan De Brazza"
    },
    {
        ", born in the Italian city of Rome in 1852. As a French naval officer he refused to work for the International African Society and instead helped the French in their conquest of the area north of the Congo River. Traveling from the Atlantic Ocean coast in present-day Gabon via the rivers ": null
    },
